                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 215.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner Lamb's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was present at the trial—she is the person.</p>
